Projects

The Good Space

This website was inspired by the COVID-19 pandemic and the simplicity of Craigslist. The name of the project is a riff off of "The Good Place" show.

I wanted to create a space for members in the community to reach out for help and receive help.

Tech Stack: Backend: Ruby on Rails, Frontend: React.js

Styling: Bootstrap, Flexbox

API: React Google Maps

Database: PostgreSQL
